{"tid":1811165,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一國兩制有冇可能實現到真普選？","createTime":"2020-01-04T12:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T22:59:38.000Z","uid":196839,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b4d280cffc11f1f04c0e7b3696116230b684b783","tid":1811165,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">一國兩制同主權在民不能並存；一國兩制前題下嘅普選，只會係假民主。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以行政長官選舉為例，《基本法》第四十五條寫明香港特別行政區行政長官須由中央人民政府任命，即使有公民提名同一人一票選舉，中央政府依舊有權凌駕民意，否決民選長官。根據中共對民選特首嘅喜好，普選有機會產生四種情況：<br />\n<blockquote>一、中央中意民眾嘅人選，但又唔任命佢，發生嘅機會好微。<br />\n二、中央反對普選出來嘅人選，並拒絕任命，就係明顯以中共意志掩蓋香港人民意志。<br />\n三、中央中意民眾嘅人選，並同意任命佢做特首。<br />\n四、中央反對普選出來嘅人選，但仍然任命佢做特首。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n情況三、四看似民主，原則上卻將「普選」降格做一場諮詢，由港人推舉嘅領導必須等到中央首肯先有實權，最終決策權依然牢固係中央手上，港人意願只供參考，並無約束力。明眼人一睇就知，共產黨冇可能比人民意志蓋過黨嘅意志，任命一個佢反對嘅特首。就算再退一步，假設中央政府真係批准人選，呢個特首權力始終來自中央，首先係對中央負責，其次先係民意，當兩者有所衝突，特首只能對中央妥協。<br />\n<br />\n以上列舉嘅四個一國兩制下普選產生嘅可能性，冇一個係實現到主權在民嘅原則。真正嘅民主，係民眾授權選出合意嘅領導人，而唔係揀一個候選人再睇下合唔合其他人意願。順從一國兩制嘅框架去爭取普選，講白啲就係向宗主國乞求民主，何況呢個宗主國更加係出名陰險毒辣、講大話唔眨眼嘅殺人政權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wfO7EhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwfO7EhG.jpg&h=8bdcfa6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n莫講話共產黨本質就係反民主嘅獨裁政權，允許香港出現真普選就等於徹底改變共黨本性，可能性微乎其微。<span style=\"color: orange;\">就算退一萬步，呢一刻中國想舒緩國際制裁，比香港實行雙普選，我地都唔可以掉以輕心，覺得一勞永逸。假使他日國際社會對香港嘅關注稍緩，制裁稍減，中國又可以反口、賴皮，一係拒絕任命民選長官製造憲政危機，一係直接廢除香港普選。</span><br />\n<br />\n重未計2047年，距離今日只係得返短短27年，到時你估「一國」會唔會咁順攤比香港人普選？上一代嘅民主回歸、一國兩制，遺毒至今，大家有目共睹。呢六個月來，好多人勇敢地企出來對抗暴政，就係唔想下一代再受我地受嘅苦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有獨立建國，係香港自己嘅國家主權下建構民主體制，香港人先有機會用民意授權領袖執政，</span>香港領導人先可以「無後顧之憂」咁服務人民、聽命於人民。呢個情況下嘅普選，先可以稱得上主權在民，真正還政於民。"},{"pid":"c95a17959f409889247418bdc066a5dd92ca1000","tid":1811165,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:28:00.000Z","msg":"source：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gwoksihokwui/photos/2867873753237049/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgwoksihokwui%2Fphotos%2F2867873753237049%2F&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLWFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=e33de772\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gwoksihokwui/photos/2867873753237049/</a>"},{"pid":"2b6114f221dbafc348ded5028724dd93315f2a95","tid":1811165,"uid":319196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:28:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d8add7cc74b5f9fe53e5bb782c9b6e35921ce369","tid":1811165,"uid":196839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港獨立 主權在民</span>"},{"pid":"8c19137b4ed421085321a5331a862b6370e9acaa","tid":1811165,"uid":319196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"93938f5112743928957c9969457544a6bc08d9e4","tid":1811165,"uid":196839,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ccah1zW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCcah1zW.jpg&h=3fe0ddea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c67c61a92bd3e2cadb10e4e4e3c686f0a327ab0a","tid":1811165,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8170200756e161c41407dfde6e16e40148274c","tid":1811165,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:42:41.000Z","msg":"選完 中央可以撒賴拒絕任命"},{"pid":"c3efabd2e2f4f2db6214350755052018fd5be7cf","tid":1811165,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">事實上基本法有好多條文幫助中國政府控制特區政府，包括DQ、釋法、單方面撤回立法會通過既法例、將中國法律以附件三形式加入香港法律等等。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有好多人覺得「有雙普選就得」、「中央其實唔係釋左好多次法」、「唔會撤回香港法律咁離譜」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">無錯，中國政府的確唔想釋咁次法，釋法的確係損害一國兩制，就係因為要避免太多釋法，所以更唔可以畀香港出現真普選。正如《逃犯條例》，中國中紀委就唔想太多秘密擄人，要將捉人地面化。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國政府可以預計，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">當立法會同特首不受中央控制，佢就要頻密釋法、撤回法律，甚至DQ，先可以保證証香港依照中國政策運作，咁會造成巨大既憲政危機，對一國兩制來講係極大尷尬，所以中國一直死守 831 決定，對獨裁者係「兩害取其輕」既做法。<br />\n</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以如果你真心希望成就香港真普選，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">必須以中國體制外作為起點思考。</span></ins></span></strong>"},{"pid":"17de07904711710ad4d0c93cfa85c9a0c86926ab","tid":1811165,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:57:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3652484a36538b32dd7532876007d34eb582b9d2","tid":1811165,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78da2817b386948a9151723727049de860aef3f","tid":1811165,"uid":196839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3efabd2e2f4f2db6214350755052018fd5be7cf","tid":1811165,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">事實上基本法有好多條文幫助中國政府控制特區政府，包括DQ、釋法、單方面撤回立法會通過既法例、將中國法律以附件三形式加入香港法律等等。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有好多人覺得「有雙普選就得」、「中央其實唔係釋左好多次法」、「唔會撤回香港法律咁離譜」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">無錯，中國政府的確唔想釋咁次法，釋法的確係損害一國兩制，就係因為要避免太多釋法，所以更唔可以畀香港出現真普選。正如《逃犯條例》，中國中紀委就唔想太多秘密擄人，要將捉人地面化。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國政府可以預計，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">當立法會同特首不受中央控制，佢就要頻密釋法、撤回法律，甚至DQ，先可以保證証香港依照中國政策運作，咁會造成巨大既憲政危機，對一國兩制來講係極大尷尬，所以中國一直死守 831 決定，對獨裁者係「兩害取其輕」既做法。<br />\n</span></ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以如果你真心希望成就香港真普選，<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">必須以中國體制外作為起點思考。</span></ins></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"所以建國獨立先係出路<br />\n對獨立有利嘅事就要做"},{"pid":"da6fb63c143e96529a127c095214dd618785f40f","tid":1811165,"uid":89160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a30f99499bf6908d3644a9ee9ef34a92b98816b","tid":1811165,"uid":194120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:11:51.000Z","msg":"冇！由頭到尾中國都只係想香港做一個名義上嘅特區實則全由中國控制，所以制造所謂[一國兩制]的大騙局讓中國在國際社會攞着數。"},{"pid":"e3890299b0fc7da47aeb37e84bcff6d2829eac90","tid":1811165,"uid":140940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"所以必須香港獨立先做到普選同五大訴求"},{"pid":"a333d3e9454243d1aa604e674921ce2dfd4a00e0","tid":1811165,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3890299b0fc7da47aeb37e84bcff6d2829eac90","tid":1811165,"uid":140940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:14:10.000Z","msg":"所以必須香港獨立先做到普選同五大訴求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T13:38:37.000Z","msg":"香港建國 立憲共和"},{"pid":"d2f7c18b3304388b5261d95ae21e124e37eb3ffa","tid":1811165,"uid":155650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:04:23.000Z","msg":"冇 因為真普選同支共口中嘅全面管治權有衝突<br />\n基於黃金六四比 民主派六 親共派四 <br />\n真普選等於佢哋失去左對香港嘅控制 <br />\n佢哋唔會接受失去控制呢一點"},{"pid":"a81658391b2f547a15739a39738345bc15b67654","tid":1811165,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:06:40.000Z","msg":"睇你地表演<br />\n係屋企睇電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ff98f158e44f5ae4d89b0da03b3897d830d496","tid":1811165,"uid":341790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:10:01.000Z","msg":"一國兩制永遠有基本法騎住<br />\n基本法又名正言順賦予中央有釋法權<br />\n所以實質就係獨裁<br />\n<br />\n某日同朋友嘅對話：<br />\n「點解你地咁荒謬信香港會獨立到？」<br />\n「荒謬得過你信唔獨立會爭取到五大訴求？」<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4057425a0d96c39428ff5ce6a5db86c48e6d962","tid":1811165,"uid":196839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0ff98f158e44f5ae4d89b0da03b3897d830d496","tid":1811165,"uid":341790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T21:10:01.000Z","msg":"一國兩制永遠有基本法騎住<br />\n基本法又名正言順賦予中央有釋法權<br />\n所以實質就係獨裁<br />\n<br />\n某日同朋友嘅對話：<br />\n「點解你地咁荒謬信香港會獨立到？」<br />\n「荒謬得過你信唔獨立會爭取到五大訴求？」<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立 唯一出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T22:59:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只有兩國  才有兩制</span></span>"}]}